                                    <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-gray-900">Q1: Are homemade products as effective as store-bought ones?</h3>
                                    <p class="text-gray-700">Yes! Ingredients like vinegar and alcohol are powerful cleaners. However, they may require a little more "elbow grease" for very old stains.</p>
                                </div>
